promptsTts.value: <speak><break time="1000ms"/>You have {{iLengthSalesOrders}} sales {{sSalesPrompt}} and {{iLengthServiceOrders}} service {{sServicePrompt}}. This is for {{sName}}, at <say-as interpret-as="address">{{sAddress1}}</say-as>{{sAddress2}}, {{sCity}}, {{sState}}, <say-as interpret-as="characters">{{sZipCode}}</say-as>. You have an upcoming appointment on {{sDate}} from <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hm12">{{sStartTime}} </say-as> until <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hm12">{{sEndTime}} </say-as></speak>
